      <title>受消费者热捧 沃尔玛上调全年业绩预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-15/walmart-raises-full-year-outlook-as-shoppers-chase-deals-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沃尔玛上调了全年销售预期，称目前预计全年净销售额将增长 4.75%，而之前的预期为增长 4%，因为该连锁店预计将吸引寻找优惠的购物者。Evercore ISI 高级董事总经理 Greg Melich 正在研究这一结果。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-15/walmart-raises-full-year-outlook-as-shoppers-chase-deals-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 12:03:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
