      <title>加拿大丰业银行与摩根大通团队合作，成立抵押贷款资本市场部门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/scotiabank-lands-jpmorgan-team-for-mortgage-capital-markets-unit</link>
